      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so it's basically just that the instant connection breaks the \"speed limit\" of the universe. but does that mean there's some kind of hidden mechanism or something we can't see that's actually doing the work, or is it truly just a fundamental part of how things work?",
